column2: SELECT   t.ra, t.dec,t.plate,t.mjd,t.fiberid,    t.petromag_u, t.petromag_g, t.petromag_r, t.petromag_i, t.petromag_z, q.petrorad_u,q.petrorad_g,q.petrorad_r,q.petrorad_i,q.petrorad_z,    g.oiii_#_eqw, g.h_alpha_eqw, g.oiii_#_flux, g.h_alpha_flux, t.z, t.objid as objid, t.specobjid as specobjid   into mydb.SDSS_gal_Chaoran FROM specphotoall as t   JOIN dbo.galSpecLine AS g ON g.specobjid = t.specobjid   JOIN dbo.photoobjall AS q ON q.objid = t.objid   where      (t.Class=&&& or t.Class=&&&)     and t.sciencePrimary>#     and t.ZWARNING=#
